description: A collection of circles in a small square formation with a semicircular formation above the top right corner; there is also a smaller rectangular formation of circles below the square formation and a very long, thin rectangular formation to the right of the other rectangular formation with a thin line of circles between the long thin rectangular formation and the bottom right corner of the square formation. Each circle has a different number in the center denoting how many lines stem from that point. There is a yellow triangle in the center of the square formation and a pale yellow triangle in the rectangular formation below the square formation.
